## ✅ Features Implemented

| Feature | Status |
|---------|--------|
| **Smart Scroll** — Automatically hides on scroll down, reappears on scroll up | ✅ |
| **Glassmorphism Design** — 90% opacity with 2xl backdrop blur effect | ✅ |
| **Animated Active Links** — Sliding gradient underline for active/hover states | ✅ |
| **Scale + Fade Dropdowns** — Ultra-smooth animations for Profile & Notifications | ✅ |
| **Dynamic Theme Toggle** — 30-degree rotation animation on sun/moon icon | ✅ |
| **Notification Badge Pop** — Scale-up animation for new unread counts | ✅ |
| **Enhanced Notifications** — Gradient icons, unread indicator, and empty state UI | ✅ |
| **Interactive Profile Menu** — Hover glow ring and user role badges (Job Seeker/Employer) | ✅ |
| **Gradient CTA Button** — Shimmering "Get Started" button with ArrowRight | ✅ |
| **Mobile Slide-in Menu** — Responsive vertical menu with staggered entrance | ✅ |
| **High Performance** — 100% CSS-only animations (no JS overhead) | ✅ |
| **v2.0 Version Badge** — Subtle identifier next to the logo | ✅ |

## 🚀 Performance & UI/UX Highlights
- **Zero Lag**: All transitions use GPU-accelerated properties (`transform`, `opacity`, `backdrop-filter`).
- **Interactive Feel**: Every interaction (hover, click, scroll) provides immediate visual feedback.
- **Modern Aesthetics**: Uses curated gradients (Purple→Pink→Orange) matching the v2.0 design system.
- **Smart Logic**: Detects scroll direction to maximize screen real estate for the user.

